data.description: Welcome to this meticulously cared for Cape Cod-style property in the heart of Springfield, Ohio. This charming home, with 1,729 square feet of living space, offers versatile living options and exudes timeless charm and modern comfort. The classic Cape Cod appeal of the exterior and pristine landscaping reflect the owners' dedication to this home.Inside, you'll discover seven spacious rooms, including a cozy living room and a well-appointed kitchen on the main level. The full basement provides ample extra storage space. The full finished attic adds to the home's versatility, allowing you to create the perfect space for your needs.In addition to the property's inherent charm, numerous upgrades enhance its functionality and value. A new fence ensures privacy and security, while the relatively new central air unit (2 years old), roof (5 years old), furnace (5 years old), and water heater (5 years old) guarantee your comfort and peace of mind. The recently updated bathroom upstairs, complete with a new shower and flooring (done just 3 months ago), adds a touch of modern luxury.Other notable upgrades include a new garage door and opener (3 years old), refreshed kitchen flooring (2 months ago), a new microwave (1 year old), and the convenience of a washer and dryer that stay on the upper level. The property also includes a trampoline for those fun-filled family moments.Lastly, you'll appreciate the gas fireplace, which operates with a remote control for effortless enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well-maintained Cape Cod beauty your own.
